* Resize Windows

  This can be used to resize the buffer with id `<number>`,
  or `0` for current buffer.

  @code bash
  :echo winwidth(<number>)
  :echo winheight(<number>)
  
  # for example
  :echo winwidth(0)
  :echo winheight(0)
  @end

  @code vim
  :lua print(vim.api.nvim_win_get_width(<number>))
  @end

  `hello-world`
